@host = http://localhost:5211
@blobName = test.txt

### Notes
# Start the app before running these requests.
# The upload request will only work if the /upload endpoint has antiforgery disabled
# or if you add a valid antiforgery token to the request.

### Upload sample text file
POST {{host}}/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=UploadBoundary

--UploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello from api.http
--UploadBoundary--

### Download blob by name
GET {{host}}/upload/{{blobName}}
